    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 8,
    "bbox": [
      71.99,
      352.55,
      413.82,
      454.33
    ],
    "text": "Write the following negative sentences and questions in Passive Voice.Eg- 1. They had not asked for any experience. Experience had not been asked for. 2. Had they asked for any particular qualifications? Had any particular qualifications been asked for?",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 8,
    "bbox": [
      71.99,
      466.96,
      437.06,
      540.73
    ],
    "text": "1. The plumber had not repaired the broken tap in the canteen.2. The lawyer had signed the document before he submitted it to the courts.3. Hadn't he paid the telephone bill before the due date?4. Had Thamara sent the invitations for the English day?5. Had Kumaran completed the work before she went to sleep?",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
